The course will give an overview of different theoretical approaches and possibilities of describing, analysing, interpreting, evaluating and understandig artworks. The role of art in developing students' critical thinking skills will be discussed. The homework consists of visiting exhibitions, reading literature, preparing and presenting presentations.Objectives/eesmärkid:  To give an overview of
- the possibilities to interpret both contemporary and historical art
- the role of art in developing critical thinking skills
